{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1558d058a0","title":"对马光斗所作搞好劳资关系报告的反映的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6a56938f05","index":0,"year":1952,"month":6,"day":2,"articleId":"1558d058a0"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"459328306e","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1558d058a0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央统战部办公室报送中央的一份材料上。这份材料说，1952年5月6日，北京市劳动局副局长马光斗在中山公园音乐堂作了关于如何搞好劳资关系的报告，资方和工人产生了不同的反应。资本家听了都很满意，认为政府明确规定了他们有三权（指财产所有权、经营管理权、用人权），保障了他们的合法权益。但有些人竞因此气焰张，对工人店员进行讽刺、打击或威胁：有些资方想找理由歇业，辞退工人；有些利用亲信打击五反中的积极分子。大多数工人店员见资方得意器张，对政策表示怀疑和不满。"},{"id":"9a9d7bde37","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1558d058a0","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共北京市委书记、北京市人民政府市长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6c6ad33691","type":"title","text":"对马光斗所作搞好劳资关系报告的反映的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1558d058a0"},{"id":"459328306e","type":"paragraph","text":"彭真同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1558d058a0"},{"id":"9a9d7bde37","type":"paragraph","text":"除资本家有三权外，应同时告诉资本家不得向工人报复，否则法办，以免引起资本家张，工人夹气","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1558d058a0"},{"id":"aea184160b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1558d058a0"},{"id":"d4907e0c02","type":"paragraph","text":"六月二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1558d058a0"}],"page":{"id":"a54b7af4cb","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1558d058a0","start":126,"end":126}}}},"__N_SSG":true}